               <p>ELEVENTH, TWELVTH, THIRTEENTH, AND FOURTEENTH<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182409160054"></xptr>COUNTS, the same as the four last, only stating the house to be in the possession of him, the said 
               <persName id="t18240916-139-person1202">
                  Robert 
                  Ball
               <interp inst="t18240916-139-person1202" type="surname" value="Ball"></interp>
